original_title: The Decade You Were Born: The 60s
overview: If you were born in the '60s, your decade opened with John F. Kennedy as the 35th President of the United States. Over 850,000 "war baby" students entered college as freshman. The cartoon The Flintstones appeared on Television for the first time.
tagline: The Decade Of Hope And Promise
title: The Decade You Were Born: The 60s
